text: In order to support and grow a talented workforce, and Michigan‚Äôs middle-class, we need to continue to support and grow CTE programs that help countless students succeed now and into the future.  Jobs for today, training for tomorrow #CTEMonth

In 2017, I joined my U.S. House colleagues in voting to pass the bipartisan Strengthening Career and Technical Education for the 21st Century Act. This will help folks develop the skills they need to compete for these in-demand jobs. More here: https://t.co/Vzzp5pjPX0 #CTEMonth

CTE ensures that competitive and skilled workers are ready, willing, & capable of holding jobs in high-wage and high-skill career fields like science, technology, engineering, art/design, mathematics, nursing, health care, construction, information technology, & more. #CTEMonth

In a globally competitive economy, workers must be prepared for skilled professions. @TheMfgInstitute says "84% of execs. agree that there is a manufacturing talent shortage in the U.S". CTE keeps the next generation competitive to keep stable, high pay careers here. #CTEMonth
